Patient Preferences for Discussing Life Expectancy: a Systematic Review.

Bjørk E(1), Thompson W(2)(3)(4), Ryg J(4)(5)(6)(7), Gaardboe O(8), Jørgensen 
TL(7)(9)(10), Lundby C(11)(2)(3)(4).

