(3)Hospital Pharmacy Funen, Odense University Hospital, Odense C, Denmark.
(4)Odense Deprescribing Initiative (ODIN), Odense C, Denmark.
(5)Department of Geriatric Medicine, Odense University Hospital, Odense C, 
Denmark.
(6)Geriatric Research Unit, Department of Clinical Research, University of 
