Projection of Impaired Life Expectancy for Individuals in the United Kingdom 
Using Estimated Excess Death Rates.

Jones DB(1), Gray NR, Reid M(2), Scott WF(3).

Author information:
(1)Bowen-Jones: Honorary Professor, Department of Health Sciences University of 
Chester CH1 4BJ.
(2)Reid: Undergraduate student Applied Mathematics at the University of 
Stirling; Computer Science and Mathematics Faculty of Natural Sciences 
University of Stirling FK9 4LA.
(3)Scott: Part-time Lecturer and Tutor Institute of Human Sciences University of 
